  "The function crosses the x-axis": "",
  "There is a point with a horizontal tangent line between a and b": "",
  "The function has a vertical tangent": "",
  "f'(c) = 0 means the tangent line at x = c is horizontal. Between two points at the same height, the curve must have at least one horizontal tangent.": "",
